data.description: Charm and convenience converge in this stunning 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow. Spanning 794 sq ft, this home balances comfort and modern living in a smartly utilized space. Step inside and immediately experience the warmth of gleaming hardwood floors that stretch throughout this cozy abode. Natural light streams through large windows, highlighting the home's well-maintained features and offering a sunny, inviting ambiance to the living spaces. The functional kitchen flows seamlessly into the dedicated dining area, creating the perfect space for entertaining. Retreat to the comfort of the well-sized bedrooms or venture into the partially finished basement, providing bonus space for endless possibilities. Outside, you’ll fall in love with the expansive deck overlooking a generously proportioned backyard. Adding to the property's charm and convenience is its advantageous location – just minutes from the highway! Don’t miss the chance to make this bungalow your new home!
